{
  "chapter": 39,
  "chapter_summary": "江别鹤以赌局赢得轩辕三光一杯酒，尽显\"江南大侠\"风范，小鱼儿随其回庄。庄院简陋，江别鹤生活清贫，小鱼儿渐生疑心。江玉郎与小鱼儿同住，小鱼儿趁夜用铜丝打开情锁，潜入后园。在花房中发现暗门，内藏伪造的燕南天藏宝图、人皮面具、毒药、银票及各门各派名单。江别鹤与江玉郎设局擒住小鱼儿，小鱼儿揭穿其伪造藏宝图的阴谋。二人互相试探推崇，江别鹤欲借刺客之手除掉小鱼儿，小鱼儿识破其借刀杀人之计。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "在下要轩辕先生做的事，方才不是已做过了么？轩辕先生的赌注既已付清，为何还要说这样的话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你说什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "输的一方，既是任凭胜方处置，在下就罚轩辕先生一杯酒，此刻轩辕先生酒已饮下，正是银货两讫，各无赊欠了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你若能杀了我，江湖中人谁不钦服，你若要我做件事，无论奇珍异宝，名马灵犬，我也可为你取来，但……但……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "但你却只是要我喝一杯酒。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "若不是在下量小，少不得还得多敬几杯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好！果然不愧是'江南大侠'！我轩辕三光平生未曾服人，今日却真的服了你江别鹤了！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "小兄弟，你的事我已管不了啦，但有'江南大侠'在此，你再也不必怕那些鼠辈欺负了，我且去了……再见！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此人倒不愧是条好汉！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_zi_chun",
      "speaker_name": "萧子春",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "此人名叫'十大恶人'，江兄不乘机将之除去，岂非太可惜了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_zi_chun",
      "text": "这样的英雄人物，世上有几个？萧兄怎能轻言'除去'两字，何况，此人除了好赌之外，并无别的恶迹。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_zi_chun",
      "speaker_name": "萧子春",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "是，小弟错了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_zi_chun",
      "text": "更何况他只要赌输，便绝不抵赖，纵然输掉头颅，也不会皱一皱眉头，试问当今天下，有他这样赌品的人，能有几个！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "只可惜轩辕三光没有听见你这番话，否则他真要感激得眼泪直流了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这位小兄莫非也是犬子好友？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "好友两字，我可实在不敢当。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这旁门左道的区区之物，我自信还能将之解开，小兄你只管随我回去……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "我也实在很想随你回去，只是这里还有人等着宰我，怎么办呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "自然都是些威名赫赫的英雄豪杰。七八个成名的大英雄等着宰我一个人，这岂非光荣之至。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我可保证，这种事以后绝不会发生了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "得名之人，谤必随之，我既不幸得名，挨些骂也是应当的，此等小人，你若去追他，岂非反令他得意？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "我小鱼儿也很少服人，今天也倒有些服你了……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这庄院昔日本是我一个好友诸葛云的，他举家迁往鲁东，就将庄院送给了我，只可惜我却无法保持它昔日的风貌，想起来未免愧对故人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "古人说：由俭入奢易，由奢入俭难，这句话我从未忘记。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "你真是个君子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难怪天下江湖中人都对你如此尊敬，一个人能忍别人之所不能忍，自然是应当成大事的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我看来看去，越看越觉得你像我昔日一位恩兄。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "哦，那是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "他如不是昔日江湖人中温文风雅的典型，也是千百年来江湖中最着名的美男子，我为小儿取'玉郎'这名字，正也是为了纪念他的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "你看我像个美男子？我这人若也可被称为'温文风雅'，那么天下的男子就没有一个不是温文风雅的了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你也许并不十分温文风雅，但你的确有他那种无法形容的魅力。尤其是你笑的时候，我不相信世上有任何少女能抗拒你微笑时瞧着她的眼睛。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "我但愿能有你说的这么好，也但愿能就是你说的那人的儿子。只可惜我爹爹也和我一样，纵然是个聪明人，但绝不是什么美男子，而且他现在也正活得好好的，也许正在他那张逍遥椅上抽着旱烟哩。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "我实在想陪你多聊聊，却又实在忍不住要去睡了……希望你明天能找几个有用的锁匠来，能将这见鬼的'情锁'打开。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这一路上我几乎已将鄂中一带有名的巧手锁匠都找过了，我实在想不到这'情锁'的机簧竟造得如此妙。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "但你只管放心，就在这两天我必定能寻得一柄削铁如泥的宝剑……到了我这里，你什么事都不必再烦心了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "所以我现在只要一沾着枕头，立刻就会睡得像死人似的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "任何人若在这种地方住上十年，不变成疯子才怪。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你放心，你用不着住十年的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你终于说话了……方才在你爹爹面前，我还以为你变成了哑巴哩。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "在我爹爹面前敢像你那样说话的人，世上只怕也没几个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "这后园你去过么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "去过一次。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你在这里也住了许久，只去过一次？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "去过一次的人，你用鞭子抽他，他也不会去第二次了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "那里面难道有鬼？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "那种地方，鬼也不敢去的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "这就是你的卧房？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "一年多没有回来，此刻看见这张床，也不觉亲热得很。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "瞧见你那些宝贝朋友之后，打死我也不相信你以前会老老实实睡在这张床上，你难道真的憋得住？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "半夜我不会溜出去么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "我自然知道大户人家的子弟，都有半夜溜出去的雅癖，但你爹爹可与别人不同，你怎能逃得过他的耳目？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你可知道我为什么要住在这屋子里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "只因这屋子距离我爹爹的卧房最远，而且窗子最多……这本来应该是佣人住的地方，但我却抢着来睡了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "据我所知，这只怕是你最聪明的选择了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你自以为聪明，其实却是个呆子，竟一直以为我真的弄不开这见鬼的'情锁'，你也不想想，我是在什么地方长大的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "伪造那藏宝图的人，果然就是他！要害得天下英雄自相残杀的人，果然就是他！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好一个大仁大义的'江南大侠'！我早知道你有不可告人的野心，否则你又怎会如此矫情，如此做作？……你不但想将天下英雄俱都瞒在鼓里，竟还想将不易收服的人俱都用计除去，好让你独霸天下！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你若不惹我，你的事我本也懒得管的，但谁叫你害得我也上了次大当，我若不教训教训你，岂非对不住自己。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我明明知道江别鹤是个厉害人物，怎地还是小估了他？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这也很好笑么？以我看来，你本该痛哭才是。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你发现了那么重要的秘密本该快快逃走才是，但你居然还能不动声色地回来，你的确有惊人的胆子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "你明明知道我已发现了你的秘密，居然还能不动声色地等我回来，等我再将自己锁起……唉，你的确了不起。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你小小年纪，居然能骗过了我，居然能找出我的秘密，这实在是我绝未想到的事，的确令人佩服。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "你竟能令天下人都相信你是个大仁大义的英雄，竟能令每个人都对你如此尊敬，当真不愧为一代枭雄。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我实在很爱惜你的才智，但你为什么偏偏要来和我作对，你既然知道了那些秘密，我纵然爱惜你，也只有忍痛割爱了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "我实在也很爱惜你的才智，很愿意见到你大事成功，但你为什么偏偏要做出那些见鬼的藏宝图来，害得我也上了次当。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你怎知道那藏宝图与我有关？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "若不是那藏宝图，我又怎会来到这里？我又怎会辛辛苦苦地来发掘你的秘密？只要你不惹到我，你的秘密关我屁事？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你什么时候知道的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "我瞧见你这'犬子'身上居然也有张藏宝图，我就问他是从哪里得来的，他说是从你书房偷来的，那时，我就想，如此重要的藏宝秘图，你怎能随便放在书房里？那时我心里就已有些疑心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你疑心得很好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "我又听人说，这'犬子'的父亲乃是一代大侠，我又想，常言道：龙生龙，凤生风，一代大侠怎会养得出如此卑鄙无耻的儿子。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你骂得也很好。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "后来我瞧见你，居然住在这种地方，居然自己搬桌子端菜，身旁只用了又聋又哑的老头子，我又想，这人若不是圣贤，就必定是我从未见过的大奸大恶之徒，因为世上只有这两种人能做出这样的事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我自然不太像是圣贤。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "所以我就一心探一探你的秘密。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你实在太聪明了，这实在是你的不幸……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "我若老些，只怕就能学会装傻了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "只可惜你只怕永远学不会了。你可知道今天晚上你并不是惟一想害我的人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "还有谁想害你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "昨夜已有人到我卧房里去过了，他先将迷香吹进来，再撬开窗子，显然是要来杀我，只可惜我昨夜并未睡在这里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "不错，你昨夜是和我一起睡在新滩口的客栈里的……但你又怎会知道有人曾经进去过你的屋子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "今天我回来时，那屋子里还有残余的迷香气味，窗台上也还留着个浅浅的足印，昨夜想来杀我的人，并不是老手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "他若是老手，今夜就不会来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "不错，只因他不是老手，所以今夜还会来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "所以你就要我睡在你屋子里，代替你被人杀死，你不但可借此杀了我，还可借此捉住那人。那么，你杀他时，还可说是为我报仇，别的人若是知道此事，少不得又要称赞你的仁义。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "和你这样聪明的孩子说话，当真有趣得很……我甚至根本不必说出来，你便已知道我的心意。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 492
    }
  ],
